{
  "stem": "24466.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- during the Lithuanians, which taking over the high ranking positions that combine the Lithuanians, were stealing a lot of goods and selling them at the market.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what they were doing later on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to shut my mouth, they were throwing to me dollars-- not to open my mouth and not to see nothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Amongst them, there was one on the name, Pikoris, Pikoris-- P-I-K-O-R-I-S.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other one was Butisas-- B-U-T-I-S-A-S.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The others, I don't remember all the number-- the-- the names.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Especially that Pikoris, always, when he was bribing me, so to say, he was throwing in me packs of dollars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the money I used to help other Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hiding it-- not in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was hiding the money actually in the factories.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one might be there still existing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It would tell a lot of stories-- that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That what I am telling you is only just a-- just a drop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whenever I need some money to help or to help for myself, I was getting help from that hiding, where the money was lying.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was amongst-- that was in one of the big drier rooms there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of the bricks were taken out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a little-- where I was hiding that-- everything there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Being in ghetto, I was helping.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You asked me who-- if I helped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was one-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-W-I-R-S-K-E I-- sorry-- I-- for Swirski.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the story, I would do this in short.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were three brothers, three of four brothers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't tell you exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I believe there are three-- there are the three brothers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they immigrated to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
